\f0\fs28 \cf0 Welcome to Pro Waiter, the first
iPhone app specifically designed for waiters

00:00:05.080 --> 00:00:06.490
and flight attendants. \
\

00:00:06.490 --> 00:00:11.920
To get started, customize the menu to reflect
your own establishment by tapping the Settings

00:00:11.920 --> 00:00:18.280
Gear Icon and navigating to the Menu. Here
you can tap the Add button to enter new menu

00:00:18.280 --> 00:00:20.710
items as well as their prices. \
\

00:00:20.710 --> 00:00:26.720
Pro Waiter gives you the ability to easily
distinguish your menu items using categories.

00:00:26.720 --> 00:00:31.670
Simply tap the Question Icon for your item
and select the category you wish to place

00:00:31.670 --> 00:00:33.469
it in. \
\

00:00:33.469 --> 00:00:39.629
Taking orders has never been easier with Pro
Waiter. Just tap the New Order button from

00:00:39.629 --> 00:00:46.809
the Home screen, enter a name for your order,
and tap New Seat. Using Pro Waiter's auto-complete

00:00:46.809 --> 00:00:54.549
function you can quickly find and input menu
items with a single tap. \

00:00:54.549 --> 00:00:56.729
\
Easily adjust the quantity of each item and

00:00:56.729 --> 00:01:02.769
enter any special notes that may be required.\
\

00:01:02.769 --> 00:01:08.130
Pro Waiter lists the details of each order
as well as automatically calculating the bill

00:01:08.130 --> 00:01:12.869
total, so you always have the answer to any
question on hand. \

00:01:12.869 --> 00:01:15.320
\
Use the Timer feature to set reminders for

00:01:15.320 --> 00:01:20.189
important events throughout the course of
a meal. No more cold soup or late checks.\

00:01:20.189 --> 00:01:23.460
\
Manage your bill settings using the Check

00:01:23.460 --> 00:01:29.670
Calculator feature. Adjust the tax for your
area, add any additional charges, and estimate

00:01:29.670 --> 00:01:34.060
the tip for each order so you always have
a goal to strive for. \

00:01:34.060 --> 00:01:37.670
\
All these features not enough? Pro Waiter

00:01:37.670 --> 00:01:43.530
has a built-in Spiels &amp; Specials notepad so
you can keep track of important information

00:01:43.530 --> 00:01:48.989
such as nightly specials and 86'd menu items.
\

00:01:48.989 --> 00:01:52.020
\
Need to share your notes? Use the email feature

00:01:52.020 --> 00:01:57.259
to keep your co-workers updated with shift
schedules and changes. \

00:01:57.259 --> 00:02:00.170
\
Download Pro Waiter for free from the App

00:02:00.170 --> 00:02:04.020
Store to start improving your service and
increasing your tips today! \

